OL,5, Energy firm BP has been fined #650,000 
OL,6, after a worker died when he plunged    
OL,7, from an offshore platform into the sea.
OL,9,FSean Anderson, 43, fell through an open
OL,10,Fgrating on the Unity installation,     
OL,11,Fabout 112 miles (180km) north-east of  
OL,12,FAberdeen, on 4 September 2014.         
OL,14,FMr Anderson, from the Tyne and Wear    
OL,15,Farea, fell about 72ft (22m) into the   
OL,16,Fwater.                                 
OL,18,FBP had been found guilty of breaching  
OL,19,Fhealth and safety laws last week by a  
OL,20,Fjury at Aberdeen Sheriff Court.        
